data.title: Damien TIMMINS Death Notice - Sydney, New South Wales
data.meta_description: TIMMINS, Damien Michael.Passed away suddenly at the age of 53 years. Damien was the loving husband of Jane, devoted dad of Gabrielle, Erica and Grace. Much loved brother of John (dec), Sharon, Peter, Mark, Dennis, Chris, Maryanne and Anthony. Loving son of Peg   Bill (both dec). Son-in-law of Marie and brother-in-law of Ross, Paul and Tim.  Forever in our hearts  A Prayer Service to Celebrate the Life of DAMIEN will be held at Holy Name Parish Catholic Church, 35 Billyard Av, Wahroonga on Monday 19th October 2015 commencing at 1:00 pm. Following Prayers, the cortege will proceed to the Macquarie Park Cemetery, Plassey Road, North Ryde, where DAMIEN will be laid to rest. In lieu of floral tributes, please consider a donation to Beyond Blue in Damien's honour. In the loving care of 904 Victoria Road,West Ryde. info@laf.com.au1300 74 00 74
